                     <interp inst="t18450818-1648-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 21 yards of tweed, value 4<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 7<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18450818-name-458" type="victimName">
